    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get there are two sides, but isn't it kind of a fact that strict sentencing doesnt actually lower crime rates in the long run? like, most sociologists say it just makes things worse for those communities. why do people still push for it if the data shows it's problematic?",
